          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "RINGR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The paraffin cube has a 3-in.-diameter hole",
                "drilled through the central axis for beam passage and",
                "placement of samples. Each ring of tubes has a",
                "different moderation thickness for neutron",
                "originating along the central axis. The ratio of",
                "neutrons detected in any one ring to those detected",
                "in any other ring is a monotonic function of neutron",
                "energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
